task.summary:
Major changes:
1. Gradient clipping 2. Reward clipping 3. NN layers same as deepmind 4. Warmup phase 5. Delayed Training
Moved statistics to it's own class. Frame skipping changed from 4 to 3.
Update batch training, fixed snapshot frequency
Fixed training issue, step now works in tensorboard
Minor improvement and bugfix for the states
No longer use cv2 to resize images, file size has been reduced as a result
Fix code after implementing target network
Fixed IO bottleneck, would save filters and weights after each update. Now only every nth episode.
Fixed total step out to reflect how many frames have been processed
small changes to load existing model
